  "body": "# ðŸ’Ž Issue\r\n\r\n### Background\r\n\r\nsignature verification was added to the slasher server endpoints in order to prevent dos attacks\r\nnevertheless having the validator sign attestations and trust the slasher not to use that attestation for slashing is risky. validator should submit the attestation before signing and DOS attack on the slasher should be handled in a different way(rate limiting for example) \r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n- [x] add two endpoints without signature verification `IsSlashableAttestationNoUpdate` and `IsSlashableBlockNoUpdate` endpoints\r\n- [ ] validator slasher verification flow change",
